reviewText: Outstanding DVD, only wish digital copies were available.

First off, the "tape" is 20+ years old and shows it. Both in the production and in equipment. There are some valuable tips, but nothing you can't find elsewhere.

This "tape" is aimed at the high volume air brushed T-shirt business. He shows you quick & dirty techniques that might work for a $25 T-shirt but little else. I really can't see this as an intro of any kind.
If you are ready for an hour or so of how to clean your airbrush than this is for you.
